ormed by a perfect fluid and a bosonic\ncondensate exist and can describe the late stages of dark matter accretion onto\nstars, in dark matter rich environments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jul 2016 15:56:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-19"}
